# Session [*] – Network+

## Main Topics
- Access Point (AP) chist? (what is AP?)  
- AP chetor kar mikonad? (how does AP work?)  

## Flashback – Access Point Basics
- AP = device ke device ha ra be network be sorat wireless vasl mikonad  >opposite< switch ke ertebat cubly vasl mikonad
- AP **data ra be wireless client ha miresand**  
- AP smart device ast, baraye wireless LAN estefade mishavad  

## Explanation
- AP = hardware baraye wireless network  
- Device ha (laptop, phone) ra be LAN ya internet vasl mikonad az tarigh Wi-Fi  
- Signal ha ra broadcast mikonad va client ha ro be network vasl mikonad  
- Estefade dar LAN haye koochik va wireless networks  

